text: Terence "Terry" Walker (29 November 1921 – 4 October 1987) was an English professional footballer who played as an inside forward in the Football League for York City, and in non-League football for Selby Town and Goole Town. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:1987 deaths Category:Sportspeople from York Category:English footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Selby Town F.C. players Category:York City F.C. players Category:Goole Town F.C. players Category:English Football League players
